Usage: [--project PROJECT] [--module MODULE] [--to TO] [--schema2] [--pretty] [--multi]
[--print-metrics] [--source-root PATH]

Available options:
        --project <PROJECT>  Path to directory with project, or to a JSON file (defaults to `.`)
        --module <MODULE>
        --to <TO>        Path to a directory where to dump result
        --schema2        Deprecated no-op.
        --pretty         Pretty print
        --multi          Output each fact separately
        --print-metrics  Print indexer metrics as JSON
        --source-root <PATH>  Prefix for every emitted `src.File` path
    -h, --help           Prints help information
